      "mechanism": null,
      "name": "Lead",
      "notes": "Same as Salesforce. NPSP rarely uses Leads in nonprofit deployments — donor onboarding typically goes directly to Contact. Leads do appear in nonprofit deployments that have a sales-like motion (corporate partnerships, sponsorship sales) where prospects get qualified before becoming partner relationships.",
